summary: AN ORDINANCE authorizing the sale by quitclaim deed of certain City (Water Department Lake Youngs Supply Line right-of-way) property in the Southwest 1/4 of the Southeast 1/4 of Section 9 and the Northwest 1/4 of the Northeast 1/4 of Section 16, Township 22 North, Range 6 East, W.M. to King County, Washington for road purposes.
